About Dead Hard: There is something called hit validation. Basically your client, your game, registers a hit on the survivor and then the server checks if the hit actually connected and if it didn't (for example because the player used Dead Hard or stunned you with a pallet), it negates the hit but your client still show that it did hit (meaning the survivor will scream and spray blood but won't go down)
